{"title":"迎着盛开的紫荆……","authors":["晏明"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":6,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着盛开的紫荆……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晏明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我追寻，追寻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个梦，一个世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦苦，苦苦追寻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾经，曾经"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在香江岸滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采撷一片片云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是一朵朵紫荆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫荆吐艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香江朗朗晴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫荆飘香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芳芬千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绵绵梦中情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦苦追寻的梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠悠，悠悠飘来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着一朵朵紫荆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那梦，那梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一团团，一团团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是血与火凝成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血与火的元素，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧红漫漫岁月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显示出伤痕与壮心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最美的梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在最美的阳光下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着盛开的紫荆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当梦成为现实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香江波涛雄浑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧簇拥着母亲……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：北京《十月》杂志社）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}